    {
      "type": "content",
      "bg": "light",
      "label": "COMPOUND CONFIGURATIONS",
      "title": "What Are Compounds?",
      "body": "Compounds let you launch multiple debug configurations at once:",
      "bullets": [
        "Group Python and JavaScript debuggers",
        "Start all services with one click",
        "Unified debugging experience",
        "Single stop terminates all"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "bg": "dark",
      "label": "COMPOUND EXAMPLE",
      "title": "Creating a Compound Config",
      "language": "json",
      "code": "{\n  \"compounds\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Full Stack Debug\",\n      \"configurations\": [\n        \"Python: FastAPI Attach\",\n        \"Chrome: Launch Frontend\"\n      ],\n      \"stopAll\": true\n    }\n  ],\n  \"configurations\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Python: FastAPI Attach\",\n      \"type\": \"debugpy\",\n      \"request\": \"attach\",\n      \"connect\": { \"port\": 5678 },\n      \"preLaunchTask\": \"Start FastAPI\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Chrome: Launch Frontend\",\n      \"type\": \"chrome\",\n      \"request\": \"launch\",\n      \"url\": \"http://localhost:5173\",\n      \"webRoot\": \"${workspaceFolder}/frontend\"\n    }\n  ]\n}",
      "tags": [
        { "text": "Compounds" },
        { "text": "Full Stack" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "bg": "light",
      "label": "PRELAUNCH TASK",
      "title": "The preLaunchTask Property",
      "body": "preLaunchTask runs a task before debugging starts:",
      "bullets": [
        "Start backend services first",
        "Wait for services to be ready",
        "Chain multiple tasks together",
        "Ensure dependencies are running"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "bg": "dark",
      "label": "FULL WORKFLOW",
      "title": "Complete One-Click Setup",
      "language": "json",
      "code": "// tasks.json\n{\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"label\": \"Start: FastAPI (debugpy on :5678)\",\n      \"type\": \"shell\",\n      \"command\": \"uv run debugpy --listen 5678 --wait-for-client -m fastapi dev --port 8081\",\n      \"isBackground\": true,\n      \"problemMatcher\": {\n        \"owner\": \"fastapi-debugpy\",\n        \"background\": {\n          \"activeOnStart\": true,\n          \"beginsPattern\": \".*FastAPI\\\\s+Starting development server.*\",\n          \"endsPattern\": \".*Application startup complete.*\"\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"label\": \"Start: Vite Dev Server\",\n      \"type\": \"shell\",\n      \"command\": \"npm run dev\",\n      \"isBackground\": true,\n      \"problemMatcher\": [\n        \"$tsc-watch\",\n        {\n          \"owner\": \"vite\",\n          \"pattern\": {\n            \"regexp\": \"^.*$\",\n            \"message\": 0\n          },\n          \"background\": {\n            \"activeOnStart\": true,\n            \"beginsPattern\": \".*VITE.*\",\n            \"endsPattern\": \".*ready in.*\"\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\n// launch.json - compound\n{\n  \"compounds\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Debug Full Stack\",\n      \"configurations\": [\n        \"Python: FastAPI Attach\",\n        \"JavaScript: Chrome\"\n      ],\n      \"stopAll\": true\n    }\n  ]\n}",
      "tags": [
        { "text": "Complete" },
        { "text": "Workflow" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "bg": "light",
      "label": "STOPALL",
      "title": "Understanding stopAll: true",
      "body": "When you stop debugging:",
      "bullets": [
        "stopAll: true terminates ALL processes in compound",
        "Clean exit for all services",
        "No orphaned processes",
        "Essential for background tasks"
      ]
    },
